<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.8.6">
<l>vēṭar maṟakkulam pōlē vēṇṭiṟṟuc ceyteṉ makaḷai</l>
<l>kūṭiya kūṭṭamē yākak koṇṭu kuṭivāḻuṅ kolō</l>
<l>nāṭum nakaruma ṟiya nallatōr kaṇṇālañ ceytu</l>
<l>cāṭiṟap pāynta perumāṉ takkavā kaippaṟṟuṅ kolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will [he] take my daughter in a consentual union</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] live together, doing whatever he wants [with her]</l>
<l rend="indent">like the angry clan of hunters?</l>
<l>Or will the lord who lept in order to break the cart</l>
<l rend="indent">get her hand in an appropriate manner [and]</l>
<l rend="indent">perform a proper marriage so that it is known</l>
<l rend="indent">to countryside and city [alike]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
